revenue_starlink.name: Starlink Revenue Calculation

revenue_launch_services.name: Launch Services Revenue
revenue_launch_services.description: Calculate revenue from launch services (volume  price per launch)
revenue_launch_services.pattern: Launch revenue = launch volume  price per launch

valuation_terminal_value.name: Terminal Value
valuation_terminal_value.description: Calculate terminal value (perpetuity or exit multiple)
valuation_terminal_value.pattern: TV = CF_final  (1 + g) / (r - g) or EBITDA  multiple

revenue_total.name: Total Revenue Aggregation
revenue_total.description: Sum all revenue streams: Starlink + Launch + Mars + Other

cost_operating.name: Operating Costs
cost_operating.pattern: Operating Costs = cost rate  revenue or fixed costs

cost_capital.name: Capital Costs
cost_capital.pattern: Capital Costs = units  cost per unit

tax_calculation.name: Tax Calculation

tax_calculation.pattern: Tax = revenue  tax_rate or profit  tax_rate

valuation_net_present_value.name: Net Present Value
valuation_net_present_value.pattern: NPV = Total Revenue - Total Costs - Taxes/Expenses

discount_irr.name: Internal Rate of Return
discount_irr.description: Calculate IRR from cash flow stream

launch_cost_per_kg.name: Launch Cost per kg
launch_cost_per_kg.description: Calculate cost per kilogram to orbit (Wright's Law)

growth_wrights_law.name: Wright's Law (Learning Curve)
